column2: SELECT   d.sdss_s_specObjId as input_specObjId, s.ra as s_ra, s.dec as s_dec, s.z as s_z,   s.specObjID as s_specObjID, s.sciencePrimary, m.* into mydb.MyTable_# from MyDB.CAGN_final_specobjid AS d      LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON d.sdss_s_specObjId=s.bestObjID      LEFT JOIN stellarMassStarFormingPort AS m ON m.specObjID=s.specObjID
